Author: KieranBoonee
Text: I relate. When I'm restricting I find it pretty easy to just.. Not eat. But when I try to eat like a normal person my body realises how hungry I actually am and I turn into a ravenous monster. Like, starving 24/7.

Author: Lovelanguagedis
Text: First day. It's the first damn day after you eat properly that the pain begins. I wake up ravenously starving now.
